gods_and_mages_engine.Items

Class KeyItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • gods_and_mages_engine.Items.BaseItem
      • gods_and_mages_engine.Items.KeyItem

  • public class KeyItem
extends BaseItem
    Used for items that cannot be removed from player inventory by normal means, nor multiples added.

    Serves as a marker to PlayerCharacter.removeItemFromInventory(String, int) to not allow removal, and to PlayerCharacter.addItemToInventory(String, int) to not allow for multiple additions.
